high_descs: Turn right, walk halfway across the room, turn left, and walk to the counter.
Turn around and walk across the room to the lamp table.
Put the pencil on the lamp table.
anns.task_desc: Put a pencil on the lamp table.

high_descs: Turn right and walk forward to the left edge of the black desk to your left.
Pick up the pencil on the desk.
Turn right and walk to the gray chair in the left corner. Turn right at the gray chair and walk to the wooden nightstand.
Put the pencil in the nightstand.
anns.task_desc: Pick up the pencil and put it on the nightstand.

high_descs: Turn right, walk to the far end of the bed, and turn left and walk to the dresser.
Pick up the pencil lying on the top of the dresser.
Turn completely around, walk to the end of the bed, turn left and walk to the wall, turn right and walk to the nightstand beside the bed.
Place the pencil on the nightstand.
anns.task_desc: Move the pencil from the dresser to the nightstand.
